properties.Text:
UPDATE ${forecast_table}
SET snow = '${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}',
	ice = '${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}',
	lightning = '${lightning:replaceNull('NULL')}',
	condition = '${condition:replaceNull('NULL')}'
WHERE prediction_date = '${prediction_date}'
AND prediction_time = '${prediction_time}'
AND location_name = 'Gwynt-y-Mor Merged'

INSERT INTO ${observation_table} (
	observation_date,
	observation_time,
	location_name,
	technology,
	snow,
	ice,
	lightning
) VALUES (
	'${observation_date}'
	,'${observation_time}'
	,'Gwynt-y-Mor Merged'
	,'${technology}'
	,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${lightning:replaceNull('NULL')}'
) ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO UPDATE
SET snow = '${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}',
	ice = '${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}',
	lightning = '${lightning:replaceNull('NULL')}'

INSERT INTO ${observation_table} (
	observation_date,
	observation_time,
	location_name,
	technology,
	visibility_km
) VALUES (
	'${observation_date}'
	,'${observation_time}'
	,'Gwynt-y-Mor Merged'
	,'${technology}'
	,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}
) ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO UPDATE
SET visibility_km = ${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}

INSERT INTO ${observation_table} (
	observation_date,
	observation_time,
	location_name,
	technology,
	significant_wave_height_m,
	maximum_wave_height_m
) VALUES (
	'${observation_date}'
	,'${observation_time}'
	,'Gwynt-y-Mor Merged'
	,'${technology}'
	,${significant_wave_height_m:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${maximum_wave_height_m:replaceNull('NULL')}
) ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_timestamp_and_location DO UPDATE
SET significant_wave_height_m = ${significant_wave_height_m:replaceNull('NULL')},
	maximum_wave_height_m = ${maximum_wave_height_m:replaceNull('NULL')}

INSERT INTO ${forecast_table} (
	prediction_date,
	prediction_time,
	location_name,
	technology,
	snow,
	ice,
	lightning,
	temperature_c,
	windspeed_m_s,
	windgusts_m_s,
	condition,
	visibility_km	
) VALUES (
	'${prediction_date}'
	,'${prediction_time}'
	,'Nordsee Ost Merged'
	,'${technology}'
	,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${lightning:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windspeed_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,${windgusts_m_s:replaceNull('NULL')} 
	,'${condition:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}
);
